"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"### \\n\\n![Avoid investing in ALTcoins that bleed against BTC / ETH](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/LY1pK6sWqepvHEQh2tyQG.png?height=500&width=1400)\\n\\nMy mouth waters as the succulent scent of profit wafts through the wires. Not forgetting the panicked frenzy of the past 6 weeks, I am eager to see where the current momentum in the market takes us. The last thing I want is to bite into a rotten apple! Let’s check that our ALTs actually aren’t bleeding against BTC or ETH! If they are, move along. It’d be better to just buy what we know to be best.\\n\\n![ADA, MATIC, BNB, CRO gained against ETH and BTC this year](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/WiEt1bmzZzJSZMltgMZaT.png?height=435&width=700)\\n\\nSince the start of the year we can see clearly ADA, MATIC, BNB, and CRO have all fared well against both ETH and BTC. \\n\\nADA — +415% vs BTC | +68% vs ETH\\n\\nMATIC — +7739% vs BTC | 2468% vs ETH\\n\\nBNB — +744% vs BTC | 176% vs ETH\\n\\nCRO — + 479% vs BTC | 89% vs ETH\\n\\n![YFI, SUSHI, and ICP bleed against ETH and BTC this year](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/qhfVT6IGiG-TSn_HIQnc1.png?height=458&width=700)\\n\\nOn the otherhand, for the most part YFI, SUSHI and ICP are bleeding against ETH and BTC this year, so be careful if you’re thinking to invest here. Buyer beware!\\n\\nI’m setting up my buy-limits as such. Let me know if you are too!\\n\\nBuy / Sell Limit Set-up — CRO Crypto.com\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/ghgOg3qDNQ3jG73MJco6d.png?height=282&width=700)\\n\\nBuy / Sell Limit Set-up — ADA Cardano\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/r2MJJd1wB9CNq5BWh8U9Q.png?height=282&width=700)\\n\\nBuy / Sell Limit Set-up — MATIC Polygon\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/YJLw-hnbSeFhGe8mOvEAL.png?height=282&width=700)\\n\\nBuy / Sell Limit Set-up — BNB Binance\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/NrOpCcQhrHYxEtYUMI3I5.png?height=282&width=700)\\n\\nMore at\\n\\n* <https://mirror.xyz/0x48e1A84CBcAB14ADe9086A4e0812D82f56d3d3C1/>\\n* [https://medium.com/@calmrat](https://medium.com/%40calmrat)\\n* <https://twitter.com/calmrat>\\n\\nTrading bonuses and more at…\\n\\n* *Crypto.com —  <https://crypto.com/exch/v4n3pauckj>*\\n* *Binance —  <https://accounts.binance.com/en/register?ref=346510770>*\\n* *Bybit —  <https://www.bybit.com/en-US/invite?ref=EKJRL>*\\n* *FTX —  <https://ftx.com/profile#a=60256726>*\",\"timestamp\":1640623735,\"title\":\"Checking ALTs for a pulse (BNB, ADA, MATIC, CRO, YFI, SUSHI, ICP)\"},\"digest\":\"GXk_8bSQYVs-8U385skamdZ16VbqRAXy68inScyJ-Vs\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x48e1A84CBcAB14ADe9086A4e0812D82f56d3d3C1\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"iOcmIo_K0T6imKJRKarJ7zH_CTfZ4TeKOnN67V8i0F4\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"ficyDnaW3mhLGYoueAcoaio4Gqw2_I9q41PQjb0ueZE\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"faFUXF2oYXY0UFqvycEMXTT-v-bLgmWSFHD1nirccHI-8GoVZqiIwUjSW11EQ9mT7ONivWfrJfv3yscIqVaXvA\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x12228965b154bbd14042c8096f46384475ad3d01611151003f7dcc356c815d5a61d3bfa47a3ecd29b9c52dbc026d09053578d615618e20dd367a187df7f01a1b1b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"iOcmIo_K0T6imKJRKarJ7zH_CTfZ4TeKOnN67V8i0F4\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"ficyDnaW3mhLGYoueAcoaio4Gqw2_I9q41PQjb0ueZE\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"GXk_8bSQYVs-8U385skamdZ16VbqRAXy68inScyJ-Vs\"}"